text: Somatidia grandis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Broun in 1895. It contains the varietas Somatidia grandis var. placita.BioLib.cz - Somatidia grandis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1895
title: Somatidia grandis
